data.description: Cute Retro Home in a quiet neighborhood. Welcome to the Mayfair Terrace community, nestled in the heart of Tucson! Just a couple yards from an elementary school. Discover this robust, brick-built home spanning 1,216 square feet, featuring two cozy bedrooms and two full bathrooms, awaiting your personal touch. Revel in the generous front and backyard spaces, complemented by a screened-in back patio -- perfect for hosting gatherings or cultivating your dream garden. This home is a blank canvas, ready for your creative vision and personal flair. Delight in the freedom of no HOA restrictions, providing ample space for all your outdoor adventures, including boats, RVs, ATVs, and more. Large office/den that could be easily made into a 3rd Bedroom. Has mountain views from large fenced backyard.
